texts.orig: Our knowledge of customers is very important to make the products we sell acceptable to them & can help solve their problems. We need to conduct customer research regularly to keep us aware of market movements & follow ongoing trends. These are the results of research that can be used as a guide to understand consumers & sell products to them better.
